[
  {"code":"basic-01","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"进行饮片性状鉴别时，应优先记录哪组信息？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"形状、表面、切面、质地和气味"},{"key":"B","text":"商品价格"},{"key":"C","text":"包装颜色"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"应保留可观察、可复核的性状证据。","dimension_code":"basic_knowledge","knowledge_point":"性状鉴别要素","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"basic-02","question_type":"true_false","stem":"只凭药材名称标签即可完成饮片性状鉴别。","options":[{"key":"T","text":"正确"},{"key":"F","text":"错误"}],"answer":"F","explanation":"标签不能替代对实物特征的观察。","dimension_code":"basic_knowledge","knowledge_point":"性状鉴别要素","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"basic-03","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"记录观察结果时，以下哪项最利于复核？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"记录拍摄条件和观察部位"},{"key":"B","text":"只写“看起来正常”"},{"key":"C","text":"删除不确定信息"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"观察条件和部位使结果可追溯。","dimension_code":"basic_knowledge","knowledge_point":"观察记录","difficulty":"intermediate"},
  {"code":"character-01","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"观察饮片切面纹理时，哪项操作更规范？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"在中性光下观察清晰的新鲜切面"},{"key":"B","text":"隔着包装判断"},{"key":"C","text":"只比较颜色深浅"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"稳定光照和清晰切面能减少误判。","dimension_code":"character_identification","knowledge_point":"切面纹理观察","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"character-02","question_type":"true_false","stem":"性状观察中的气味可以作为综合鉴别证据之一。","options":[{"key":"T","text":"正确"},{"key":"F","text":"错误"}],"answer":"T","explanation":"气味应与形态等证据联合使用。","dimension_code":"character_identification","knowledge_point":"气味观察","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"character-03","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"图片中切面不清晰时，应如何处理？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"补充清晰图像后复核"},{"key":"B","text":"直接确定名称"},{"key":"C","text":"忽略切面特征"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"不足的视觉证据应触发补充与复核。","dimension_code":"character_identification","knowledge_point":"切面纹理观察","difficulty":"intermediate"},
  {"code":"similar-01","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"两个相似饮片候选置信度接近时，优先采取什么措施？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"补充差异特征后复核"},{"key":"B","text":"无条件选排序第一项"},{"key":"C","text":"隐藏候选项"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"接近候选需要更多可解释证据。","dimension_code":"similar_medicine","knowledge_point":"相似饮片复核","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"similar-02","question_type":"true_false","stem":"相似药材复核时，应记录区分候选的关键特征。","options":[{"key":"T","text":"正确"},{"key":"F","text":"错误"}],"answer":"T","explanation":"区分特征可支持后续复核和学习。","dimension_code":"similar_medicine","knowledge_point":"差异特征","difficulty":"basic"},
  {"code":"similar-03","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"候选项间存在冲突证据时，应怎样记录？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"保留冲突和人工复核需求"},{"key":"B","text":"删除较弱候选"},{"key":"C","text":"改写为确定结论"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"不确定性必须明确保留。","dimension_code":"similar_medicine","knowledge_point":"相似饮片复核","difficulty":"intermediate"},
  {"code":"pharma-01","question_type":"single_choice","stem":"形成可追溯的药典依据时，应记录什么？","options":[{"key":"A","text":"版本、条目位置和证据原文"},{"key":"B","text":"“网上查到”"},{"key":"C","text":"只保留结论"}],"answer":"A","explanation":"来源版本与位置是复核基础。","dimension_code":"pharmacopoeia_rules","knowledge_point":"药典证据引用","difficulty":"basic"},
